snippet.title: LawnInvaders Trailer
snippet.description:
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.AlexOD.LawnInvaders
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Aldonn_

Music: Seventh Gear - Suffer

The year is 2075, join everybody's favourite millennial gaming grandpa as he fends off creatures he hallucinates after doing nothing but play games his entire life.

Inspired by Pyoro/Bird & Beans, LawnInvaders expands on the game-play by introducing platforming and alternative enemies/bosses to shoot down.

Features:
- 8 types of enemies
- 2 bosses
- 15+ backgrounds
